songs.title: Oceans - live at e-werk, cologne
songs.lyrics:
Wait for your call, love
The call never came
Ready to fall, love
Ready to claim
I'm ready for it all, love
I'm ready for a pain
Meet under sun
Meet me again
In the rain
In the rain
In the rain
The rain
Behind the walls, love
I'm trying to change
And I'm ready for it all, love
I'm ready for a change
Meet under blue sky
Meet me again
In the rain
The rain, the rain
In the rain
The rain
Got to find yourself alone in this world
You've got to find yourself alone
